title: Glorch's Great Escape: Walking is for Chumps
description: What is this game?Glorch's Great Escape is a challenging puzzle platformer where your only weapon is the almighty Telenade, a grenade with a built-in teleporter. Guide Glorch from his prison cell through the defenses of his captor's space station, and help him escape on his impounded ship.You'll be solving plenty of difficult platforming puzzles and scenarios, finding some secrets, smashing a few robots, and generally dying a whole bunch of times.
